            <div class="sh-msg-title">Welcome to StyleHub Miami!</div>
            <div class="sh-msg-text">Thank you for creating your account. If you need help with anything, our support team is here for you.</div>
          </div>
          <div class="sh-msg-time">Welcome</div>
        </div>
        <div style="text-align:center;padding:16px 0;color:var(--text2);font-size:12px">
          Need help? <a href="/pages/help-center" style="color:var(--red)">Visit our Help Center</a> or use the chat widget below.
        </div>
      </div>
