          <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="var(--navy)" stroke-width="1.5" width="48" height="48"><path d="M1 12s4-8 11-8 11 8 11 8-4 8-11 8-11-8-11-8z"/><circle cx="12" cy="12" r="3"/></svg>
          <h3>No recently viewed products</h3>
